Step 1: Prerequisites
Before Spring Boot, make sure you know:

Java Basics — https://www.w3schools.com/java/
Java OOP Concepts — https://www.javatpoint.com/java-oops-concepts
Maven/Gradle basics — https://maven.apache.org/guides/getting-started/
Basic SQL — https://www.w3schools.com/sql/
Step 2: Spring Core Fundamentals
Understand IoC, Dependency Injection, and Beans first.

Spring Core - Baeldung — https://www.baeldung.com/spring-tutorial
Spring Framework Docs — https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/current/reference/html/core.html
YouTube - Java Brains Spring Core — https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLC97BDEFDCDD169D7
Step 3: Spring Boot Basics
Official Getting Started Guide — https://spring.io/guides/gs/spring-boot/
Spring Initializr — https://start.spring.io
Baeldung Spring Boot — https://www.baeldung.com/spring-boot
YouTube - Amigoscode Spring Boot — https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9SGDpanrc8U
Step 4: Building REST APIs
Spring MVC REST Guide — https://spring.io/guides/gs/rest-service/
Baeldung REST with Spring — https://www.baeldung.com/rest-with-spring-series
YouTube - Daily Code Buffer — https://www.youtube.com/c/DailyCodeBuffer
Step 5: Database — Spring Data JPA & Hibernate
Spring Data JPA Guide — https://spring.io/guides/gs/accessing-data-jpa/
Baeldung JPA — https://www.baeldung.com/the-persistence-layer-with-spring-data-jpa
Hibernate Docs — https://hibernate.org/orm/documentation/
Step 6: Spring Security
Spring Security Docs — https://docs.spring.io/spring-security/reference/
JWT with Spring Boot - Baeldung — https://www.baeldung.com/spring-security-jwt
YouTube - Amigoscode Spring Security — https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=her_7pa0vrg
Step 7: Exception Handling & Validation
Global Exception Handling - Baeldung — https://www.baeldung.com/exception-handling-for-rest-with-spring
Bean Validation Guide — https://www.baeldung.com/javax-validation
Step 8: Testing
Spring Boot Testing Docs — https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/current/reference/html/features.html#features.testing
JUnit 5 Guide — https://junit.org/junit5/docs/current/user-guide/
Mockito — https://site.mockito.org/
Baeldung Testing — https://www.baeldung.com/spring-boot-testing
Step 9: Docker & Deployment
Dockerizing Spring Boot - Baeldung — https://www.baeldung.com/dockerizing-spring-boot-application
Spring Boot Docker Guide — https://spring.io/guides/gs/spring-boot-docker/
YouTube - TechWorld with Nana Docker — https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3c-iBn73dDE
Step 10: Microservices & Spring Cloud
Spring Cloud Docs — https://spring.io/projects/spring-cloud
Microservices with Spring Boot - Baeldung — https://www.baeldung.com/spring-microservices-guide
YouTube - Java Techie Microservices — https://www.youtube.com/c/JavaTechie
